I"]<h1 id="dbms">DBMS</h1>

<p class="fs-6 fw-300">Database management system or DBMS in short is a technology to store, retrieve, manage data.</p>

<hr />

<p>Typically it&#8217;s a software which allows us to do all those things. There are various DBMS softwares out there some of them are <strong>Postgres</strong>, <strong>MySQL</strong>, <strong>SQLite</strong>.</p>

<p>DBMS makes following thigs easy for us:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Data definition</strong></li>
  <li><strong>Data updation</strong></li>
  <li><strong>Data retrieval</strong></li>
  <li><strong>User Administration</strong></li>
</ul>
